      <title>穆迪评级下调后塞内加尔欧元债券延续跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/senegal-eurobonds-extend-losses-after-moody-s-ratings-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪将塞内加尔的信用评级进一步下调至垃圾级，并将其列入进一步降级的观察名单，此后塞内加尔的欧元债券周一扩大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/senegal-eurobonds-extend-losses-after-moody-s-ratings-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 12:20:34 GMT</pubDate>
